    "plan_content": "The plan is ready for your review. Here's a quick summary of what it covers:\n\n**4 files to touch:**\n\n1. **`crates/uv-cli/src/lib.rs`** — Add `Stats(StatsArgs)` variant to `CacheCommand` enum + define `StatsArgs` struct (mirrors `SizeArgs` with `--human` flag)\n2. **`crates/uv/src/commands/cache_stats.rs`** — New file implementing the core logic: iterates `CacheBucket::iter()`, computes per-bucket disk usage via `DiskUsage`, prints each bucket's size then a total line\n3. **`crates/uv/src/commands/mod.rs`** — Add `mod cache_stats;` declaration and `pub(crate) use cache_stats::cache_stats;` re-export\n4. **`crates/uv/src/lib.rs`** — Add dispatch arm matching `CacheCommand::Stats(args)` calling `commands::cache_stats(&cache, args.human, printer)`\n\nThe implementation reuses all existing infrastructure (`CacheBucket::iter()`, `Cache::bucket()`, `DiskUsage`, `human_readable_bytes`, `Display for CacheBucket`) — no new dependencies needed.",
